[{"id": 487, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loyal to a Fault</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You've never needed a reason beyond: they're yours.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you make clear, without qualification, that you're with someone. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I decided I'd never leave someone alone in it after <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 488, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">The Levity</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You know when the room needs to breathe.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you ease tension with something light \u2014 a joke, a story, a moment of warmth. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I found out that lightness can help when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 489, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Quiet Respect</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You don't say much. What you do say lands.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you name something specific you noticed or respect about someone. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I learned what it meant to actually be seen when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 490, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">The Protector</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">It's not about strength. It's about who you put yourself in front of.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you commit, plainly, to facing whatever comes next with someone rather than letting them face it alone. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I first stood in front of something when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 491, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Honest Mirror</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You tell people the truth because you respect them too much not to.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you tell someone something true and necessary, even when it's uncomfortable. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">Someone told me a hard truth and it changed me when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 492, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bond acc-bond\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Bond</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">The Witness</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You remember. You always remember.</div><div class=\"bf-eff\">Start a conversation where you tell someone specifically what you've seen them do or endure. If it lands, you both gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Bond</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I started holding onto moments like this after <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 493, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hot-Headed</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I know I'm quick to ignite. I always have been.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Let it happen</strong> \u2014 Narrate your reaction. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold it in</strong> \u2014 All Speak <strong>Actions</strong> have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You act on it, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who takes a breath first.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> sets me off.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 494, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Phobia</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I've faced plenty of things. This just isn't one of them.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Give in to it</strong> \u2014 Narrate your reaction. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Force it down</strong> \u2014 All checks near the trigger have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You face it fully, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who stands tall.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> makes my skin crawl.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 495, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Greedy</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I'm not proud of it. But I'd do it again.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Take it</strong> \u2014 Narrate what you go for. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Resist it</strong> \u2014 All Bargain <strong>Actions</strong> have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You walk away from it, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who has enough.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> is right there for the taking.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 496, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Haunted</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">The past has a way of showing up uninvited.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Let it surface</strong> \u2014 Narrate the memory. Allies <strong>Draw</strong> 1 card. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Push it down</strong> \u2014 All Mind rolls have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You confront it, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who finally looks it in the eye.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> takes me back.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 497, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Stubborn</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">Once I've made up my mind, that's usually the end of the conversation.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold your ground</strong> \u2014 Your course is locked \u2014 see it through. Related rolls are yours alone.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Concede \u2014 barely</strong> \u2014 The GM makes one free move for your reluctance.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> Your position proves correct, is proven wrong, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who changes their mind.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I won't back down when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 498, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Soft-Hearted</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I know I can't fix everything. I just can't ignore it either.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Drop everything</strong> \u2014 Your next <strong>Action</strong> must address their need. GM makes one free move elsewhere.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Look away</strong> \u2014 All <strong>Actions</strong> this <strong>Scene</strong> have disadvantage.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You help them, they're beyond help, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who knows when to let go.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"><span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> is where the armor comes off.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 499, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Paranoid</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I don't assume the worst. Experience just keeps teaching me it's usually right.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Act on it</strong> \u2014 Narrate your suspicion. GM makes one free move \u2014 right or wrong.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Say nothing</strong> \u2014 Ally Help <strong>Actions</strong> are unavailable while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> The threat proves real or baseless, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who lets people in.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">When <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span>, the walls go up.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 500, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Reckless</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I never think it's going to go wrong. That's always been the problem.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Throw yourself in</strong> \u2014 Narrate acting without thinking. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold yourself back</strong> \u2014 All checks have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> It pays off or costs you something real, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who looks before they leap.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"><span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> is when they stop thinking.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 501, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Vengeful</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I remember everything. Every slight, every score I haven't settled.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Act on it</strong> \u2014 Narrate old anger rising. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Suppress it</strong> \u2014 Helping characters connected to the trigger is unavailable while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You let it go, exact the cost, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who lets it rest.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">When <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span>, old scores resurface.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 502, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Vain</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I always know how this looks. That's never been the comfort you'd think.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>React visibly</strong> \u2014 Narrate protecting your image. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold it together</strong> \u2014 All subtle or hidden <strong>Actions</strong> have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> Your reputation holds, you accept the hit, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who doesn't need the mirror.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"><span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> is when the mask slips.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 503, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Jealous</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I don't hate them. I just can't stop wanting what they have.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Make it visible</strong> \u2014 Narrate your envy openly. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Suppress it</strong> \u2014 All cooperation with that person has disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> You get it, let it go, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who cheers them on.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> and I want what they have.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 504, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-flaw acc-flaw\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Flaw</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bloodlust</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">I don't go looking for it. But I stop looking away from it.</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Push toward conflict</strong> \u2014 Narrate escalating tension. The GM makes one free move.</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold back</strong> \u2014 All Speak <strong>Actions</strong> targeting de-escalation have disadvantage while held.</div></div><div class=\"bf-dismiss\"><strong>Dismiss:</strong> The conflict resolves or you back down, or an ally <strong>Cleanses</strong> it. \u2014 The version of you who walks away.</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"bf-stem\"> <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span> and I want to settle this with force.</div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 505, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Human</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You were not born with magic or ancient lineage. You were born with will.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When drive, adaptability, or sheer human determination tips the balance,</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Press On</strong> &mdash; name what you're reaching toward \u2014 your ambition shapes what happens next</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Find a Way</strong> &mdash; improvise, adapt, or simply refuse to be stumped; the GM confirms what opens up</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Burn Bright</strong> &mdash; throw yourself in completely and succeed \u2014 the GM names what it costs you</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I found out what I was capable of when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 506, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Elf</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">Something in you is older than this world, and it always notices.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">While this card is in your hand, once per <strong>Scene</strong> attune to your surroundings and ask one:</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">My lineage opened my perception to <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 507, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Dwarf</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You were carved from stone and stubbornness \u2014 and it shows.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When a blow \u2014 physical, social, or emotional \u2014 would stagger someone else,</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Absorb It</strong> \u2014 take it and stay standing; you don't let the cost show</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Shake It Off</strong> \u2014 make a <strong>Luck Check</strong> \u2014 on a success, your resilience turns the tide</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Dig In</strong> \u2014 your refusal to be moved becomes a statement the <strong>Scene</strong> must acknowledge</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I learned what I was made of when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 508, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Halfling</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You've gotten away with things that should have ended you more times than you can count.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">Once per <strong>Scene</strong>, when you fail any check,</div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">The most unbelievable time luck found me was <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 509, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Half-Orc</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have been underestimated your whole life. You have learned to use that.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When the <strong>Scene</strong> demands you give in, fall, or yield \u2014</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Relentless</strong> \u2014 stay standing on pure will; narrate how you refuse to go down</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Show Your Fury</strong> \u2014 let your heritage surface; the room recalibrates around what it just saw</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Survivor's Advantage</strong> \u2014 your familiarity with being hit gives you <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> on your very next roll</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">People expected less from me, and I used that when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 510, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Tiefling</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You carry something ancient and unholy in your blood. It is not a curse. It is yours.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When your fiendish heritage \u2014 the unease you inspire, the fire in your blood \u2014</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Cast the Shadow</strong> \u2014 your presence unsettles; name exactly what shifts in the <strong>Scene</strong></div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Dark Gift</strong> \u2014 spend a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> to gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> on any one roll this <strong>Scene</strong></div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Infernal Tongue</strong> \u2014 something in this <strong>Scene</strong> answers to what you carry; the GM confirms what opens</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">I stopped running from what I am when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 511, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Dragonborn</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">Every choice you make is an answer to the question of what your bloodline means.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When the full weight of your draconic heritage \u2014 elemental, ancestral, primal \u2014</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Breath</strong> &mdash; unleash what runs in your veins; all in range must respond, evade, or endure</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Dragon's Bearing</strong> &mdash; your stillness, your voice, your presence changes the room's temperature</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Scaled</strong> &mdash; your natural resistance means a threat that stops others doesn't land the same on you</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">dragon_special <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 512, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Gnome</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">Your mind moves in directions that simply do not occur to anyone else.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When cleverness, invention, or an angle nobody spotted changes what's possible,</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Lateral Thinking</strong> \u2014 see the solution others missed; name it \u2014 the GM confirms it works</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Tinker's Touch</strong> \u2014 use something in this <strong>Scene</strong> in a way its maker never intended</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Gnomish Cunning</strong> \u2014 when magic or deception is aimed at you, gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> to resist or see through it</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">The thing that surprises people most about how I think is <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 513, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Half-Elf</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You belong to neither world completely. You have learned to make that a strength.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When being a bridge \u2014 between peoples, cultures, or ways of seeing \u2014 matters,</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Common Ground</strong> &mdash; find the thread connecting two apparently opposed parties; name it and they both feel it</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Read the Room</strong> &mdash; your experience across cultures means you know the rules here; act on it</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Best of Both</strong> &mdash; name which heritage you're drawing on \u2014 elven grace or human drive \u2014 and show it</div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">Living between two worlds gave me <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 514, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-ancestry acc-ancestry\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Ancestry</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Orc</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You are built for things that require more than most people have.</div><div class=\"bf-trig\">When raw power, momentum, or the force of your presence is what the moment needs,</div><div class=\"bf-choose\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Rush</strong> \u2014 your momentum carries the <strong>Scene</strong>; name what breaks or gives way before you</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Tower</strong> \u2014 plant yourself and refuse to move; your mass and will make you a wall the <strong>Scene</strong> works around</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Battle Cry</strong> \u2014 your voice carries something older than words; all allies who hear it gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> on their next <strong>Action</strong></div></div><div class=\"bf-stem-label\">Origin</div><div class=\"bf-stem\">The strength in me was forged when <span class=\"bf-fill\"></span></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 529, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Fey Patron</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">A creature of delight and cruelty, bound to the old wild places.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\" style=\"gap:3px;padding:5px 10px;\"><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">The Marks of</div><div class=\"marks-row\" style=\"gap:2px;\"><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Whimsy</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">2</span><strong>Charm</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">3</span><strong>Trick</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">4</span><strong>Glamour</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">5</span><strong>Thorns</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">6</span><strong>\u2605 Choose</strong></div></div><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">Invoke Their Name</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:9px;line-height:1.4;\">Call them forth and select one of the <strong>Marks</strong> above to warp the <strong>Scene</strong> in your favor. Then <strong>Shuffle</strong> this card into your <strong>Draw</strong> Pile.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div style=\"background:rgba(138,32,16,0.08);border:0.5px solid rgba(138,32,16,0.3);border-radius:3px;padding:3px 5px;\"><div class=\"bane-label\" style=\"font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:6px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a2010;margin-bottom:1px;\">\ud83d\udd12 Bane \u2014 To Clear This:</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;line-height:1.4;color:#8a2010;font-style:italic;\">Announce that your Patron has arrived. Roll a d6 to determine which <strong>Mark</strong> you must pay. The GM decides the cost before this <strong>Scene</strong> ends.</div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 530, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">The Old One</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">A vast intelligence that does not notice you, except when it does.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\" style=\"gap:3px;padding:5px 10px;\"><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">The Marks of</div><div class=\"marks-row\" style=\"gap:2px;\"><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Glimpse</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">2</span><strong>Consume</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">3</span><strong>Void</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">4</span><strong>Unraveling</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">5</span><strong>Silence</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">6</span><strong>\u2605 Choose</strong></div></div><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">Invoke Their Name</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:9px;line-height:1.4;\">Call them forth and select one of the <strong>Marks</strong> above to warp the <strong>Scene</strong> in your favor. Then <strong>Shuffle</strong> this card into your <strong>Draw</strong> Pile.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div style=\"background:rgba(138,32,16,0.08);border:0.5px solid rgba(138,32,16,0.3);border-radius:3px;padding:3px 5px;\"><div class=\"bane-label\" style=\"font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:6px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a2010;margin-bottom:1px;\">\ud83d\udd12 Bane \u2014 To Clear This:</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;line-height:1.4;color:#8a2010;font-style:italic;\">Announce that your Patron has arrived. Roll a d6 to determine which <strong>Mark</strong> you must pay. The GM decides the cost before this <strong>Scene</strong> ends.</div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 531, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Celestial Patron</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">A being of order and light that found you useful, or worthy.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\" style=\"gap:3px;padding:5px 10px;\"><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">The Marks of</div><div class=\"marks-row\" style=\"gap:2px;\"><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Mercy</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">2</span><strong>Radiance</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">3</span><strong>Truth</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">4</span><strong>Shield</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">5</span><strong>Reckoning</strong></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">6</span><strong>\u2605 Choose</strong></div></div><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">Invoke Their Name</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:9px;line-height:1.4;\">Call them forth and select one of the <strong>Marks</strong> above to warp the <strong>Scene</strong> in your favor. Then <strong>Shuffle</strong> this card into your <strong>Draw</strong> Pile.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div style=\"background:rgba(138,32,16,0.08);border:0.5px solid rgba(138,32,16,0.3);border-radius:3px;padding:3px 5px;\"><div class=\"bane-label\" style=\"font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:6px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a2010;margin-bottom:1px;\">\ud83d\udd12 Bane \u2014 To Clear This:</div><div c